edu.umn.se.trap.form
Class AllUserForms

java.lang.Object
  edu.umn.se.trap.form.AllUserForms

public class AllUserForms
extends java.lang.Object

This class manages all the users forms of the TRAP system. It holds both forms that are in progress and forms that have been successfully processed. While feasible, there should be only one instance of this class.

Author:
nagell2008
